latestPosts.caption:
Just an hour from Mumbai and two from Pune, I found the perfect weekend escape at Karjat – Discover Resort 🌿✨ Surrounded by lush greenery, it’s the kind of place where you don’t have to worry about a thing — just arrive and relax. From pool parties and rain dances to DJ nights and fun family activities, there’s never a dull moment. The food was delicious, the ambience was warm, and the service was absolutely amazing. If you’re looking to unwind with your family, discover resort karjat is the place. Highly recommended for anyone who wants fun, peace, and good vibes all in one spot! 💚☀️
